wn":false},{"_id":"MxnWDZnkyj0Br5YZ","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The caster becomes an aquatic creature for as long as he remains in the water. He can breathe water and air with equal ability, move normally underwater, suffer no damage from pressures found at extreme depths, and can speak with any intelligent aquatic creature. All of his possessions are protected from submersion. <br /><br />As a creature of the water, the caster gains a +2 bonus to all rolls made while in the water. Additionally, any creature that holds the caster's hand gains the same benefit as long as contact is maintained. The duration of this transformation is permanent or until the caster completely exits the water and steps foot on dry land once again.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":64,"range":[36,99],"drawn":false}],"formula":"1d20","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true}
{"_id":"i74ye1hbS4L3aSr0","name":"Magic Shield","permission":{"default":0,"U5X07uKi3FMVWkQ1":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.dcc-compendiums.dcc-spell-tables.GGF7KLdDmALjilhs"}},"img":"modules/dcc-core-book/assets/svg/game-icons-net/shield-reflect.svg","description":"<h1>Magic Shield</h1><p><strong>Level:</strong> 1</p><p><strong>Range:</strong> Touch</p><p><strong>Duration:</strong> Varies</p><p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 action</p><p><strong>Save:</strong> None</p><p><strong>Page:</strong> 146</p><br><p>The caster conjures up a magical shield that defends him from opponents.</p><br><p><strong>Spell Data:</strong> @Compendium[dcc-core-book.dcc-core-spell-journals.Magic Shield]{Magic Shield}</p>","results":[{"_id":"M8GjvyWNWaLySnmr","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Lost, failure, and worse! Roll [[/roll 1d6]] modified by Luck: (0 or less) corruption + misfire; (1-2) corruption; (3+) misfire.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[-99,1],"drawn":false},{"_id":"DYz1o99NwHg890Yw","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Lost. Failure.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[2,11],"drawn":false},{"_id":"pud3jxgzLbTPNlv6","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The caster conjures a weak shield that provides a +2 bonus to AC for [[/roll 1d6]] rounds.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[12,13],"drawn":false},{"_id":"kCQhygPwQPPrLWl8","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The caster conjures a shield that provides a +4 bonus to AC for [[/roll 2d6]] rounds.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[14,17],"drawn":false},{"_id":"mV1smfdSCtKiUXYv","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The caster conjures shield that provides a +4 bonus to AC for [[/roll 1d3]] turns. When casting the spell, the caster can apply the shield to himself or one ally touched.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[18,19],"drawn":false},{"_id":"LlugZzawEATGZsHm","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The caster conjures a shield that provides a +4 bonus to AC for [[/roll 1d3]] turns. When casting the spell, the caster can apply the shield to himself or one ally touched. In addition to the AC bonus, the shield also blocks magic missiles automatically (missiles usually have no effect; see magic missile spell description).","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[20,23],"drawn":false},{"_id":"0huwl3WV5bnpVZe7","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The caster conjures a shield that protects him or an ally touched. The shield lasts [[/roll 1d4+1]] turns and has three benefits: it provides a +4 bonus to AC; it blocks magic missiles automatically (see magic missile spell description); and it blocks most attacks from mundane projectiles, reducing damage from any arrow, sling stone, bolt, dart, or other ranged weapon by 10 points per attack for the duration of the spell.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[24,27],"drawn":false},{"_id":"xkc8FYsX9255W8JA","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The caster conjures two shields that protect him and one ally touched. Each shield lasts [[/roll 1d4]] hours and has four benefits: it provides a +4 bonus to AC; it blocks magic missiles automatically (see magic missile spell description); it blocks most attacks from mundane projectiles, reducing damage from any arrow, sling stone, bolt, dart, or other ranged weapon by 10 points per attack for the duration of the spell; and it provides a benefit in counterspelling equal to a +2 bonus to any subsequent spell check made as a counterspell.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[28,29],"drawn":false},{"_id":"Lj5emVbphMWU20dg","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The caster conjures a battalion of magical shields that protect him and his allies. The caster is automatically shielded, as are all allies within a 10' radius. Each shield lasts [[/roll 1d4+1]] hours and follows the allies even if they leave the caster's side. <br /><br />Each shield has four benefits: it provides a +6 bonus to AC; it blocks magic missiles automatically (see magic missile spell description); it blocks most attacks from mundane projectiles, reducing damage from any arrow, sling stone, bolt, dart, or other ranged weapon by 20 points per attack for the duration of the spell; and it provides a benefit in counterspelling equal to a +4 bonus to any subsequent spell check made as a counterspell.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[30,31],"drawn":false},{"_id":"fuTvC6EJ9mUHPLmU","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The caster calls forth a globe of shimmering magical energies that protects him and his allies. The caster is automatically encased in this magical shield, as are all allies within a 10' radius. The shimmering globes last until the next sunrise and follow the allies even if they leave the caster's side. <br /><br />Each globe has five benefits: it provides a +8 bonus to AC; it blocks magic missiles automatically (see magic missile spell description); it reduces damage on all attacks against its target by 2 points; it blocks most attacks from mundane projectiles, reducing damage from any arrow, sling stone, bolt, dart, or other ranged weapon by 20 points per attack for the duration of the spell; and it provides a benefit in counterspelling equal to a +4 bonus to any subsequent spell check made as a counterspell","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[32,99],"drawn":false}],"formula":"1d20","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true}
{"_id":"iLRe2VWOvcW3CIyB","name":"Control Ice","permission":{"default":0,"U5X07uKi3FMVWkQ1":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.dcc-compendium.spell-tables.9JpmDgnyGwlMPR8U"}},"img":"modules/dcc-core-book/assets/svg/game-icons-net/frozen-block.svg","description":"<h1>Control Ice</h1><p><strong>Level:</strong> 4</p><p><strong>Range:</strong> 20' per caster level</p><p><strong>Duration:</strong> Varies</p><p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 action</p><p><strong>Save:</strong> Fort partial (sometimes)</p><p><strong>Page:</strong> 239</p><br><p>The caster creates ice walls or blasts of frigid cold to hinder or harm his enemies. On a successful casting, the caster may choose to invoke any effect of equal to or less than his spell check, allowing a range of options with every successful casting to produce a weaker but potentially more useful result.</p><br><p><strong>Spell Data:</strong> @Compendium[dcc-core-book.dcc-core-spell-journals.Control Ice]{Control Ice}</p>","results":[{"_id":"hQgUOvXBrJ0mBICt","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Lost, failure, and worse! Roll [[/roll 1d6]] modified by Luck: (0 or less) corruption + patron taint + misfire; (1-2) corruption; (3) patron taint (or corruption if no patron); (4+) misfire.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[-99,1],"drawn":false},{"_id":"dS2y05SVKpmAXlOh","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Lost. Failure.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":10,"range":[2,11],"drawn":false},{"_id":"RJV960dvTl8YfT4w","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Failure, but spell is not lost.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":6,"range":[12,17],"drawn":false},{"_id":"AcjpvWhbpjH92olq","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The caster blasts an area 40' in diameter with frigid sleet, doing  [[/roll 2d6]]+CL damage (Fort save for half) to creatures caught in its area of effect. Affected creatures are also blinded and their movement is reduced by half. Creatures attacking or moving within the area must make a Ref save or slip and fall prone. Sleet melts in [[/roll 1d4+2]] rounds.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":2,"range":[18,19],"drawn":false},{"_id":"0jv7W0CY9TwOjNEr","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The caster blast an area 40' in diameter with frigid sleet, doing  [[/roll 3d10]]+CL damage (Fort save for half) to creatures caught in its area of effect. Affected creatures are also blinded and their movement is reduced by half. Creatures attacking or moving within the area must make a Ref save or slip and fall prone. Sleet melts in [[/roll 1d6+2]] rounds.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":4,"range":[20,23],"drawn":false},{"_id":"DhlLtAoUqrPWOcos","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The caster conjures a vertical wall of solid ice to bar his enemies' passage and protect his allies. The wall is 1\" thick per caster level and up to 10' square per caster level. Opponents can break through the wall with a Strength check vs. spell check DC but suffer [[/roll 1d4]]+CL points of cold damage per round while doing so. The wall lasts for 1 turn per caster level. Magical fire destroys the wall in a single round.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":2,"range":[24,25],"drawn":false},{"_id":"W7F8EWomm0MXqe4j","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The caster conjures a vertical wall of solid ice to bar his enemies' passage and protect his allies. Additionally, the wall emits painful waves of cold from the side opposite the caster. All within 30' of the wall suffer [[/roll 1d4]]+CL damage each round. The wall is 1\" thick per caster level and up to 10' square per caster level. <br /><br />Opponents can break through the wall with a Strength check vs. spell check DC but suffer  [[/roll 1d6]]+CL points of cold damage per round while doing so. The wall lasts for 1 turn per caster level. Magical fire destroys the wall in a single round.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":3,"range":[26,28],"drawn":false},{"_id":"OEU41z5qkBxIbNOy","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The caster creates a cone of sub-zero cold that drains the heat from all creatures in its area of effect. The cone is 20' long per caster level and has a width of 10' per caster level at its terminus. Victims suffer [[/roll 1d12]] damage per caster level with no save.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":5,"range":[29,33],"drawn":false},{"_id":"KtqQQdDTdoWwaPR8","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The caster creates a cone of sub-zero cold that drains the heat from all creatures in its area of effect. The cone is 20' long per caster level and has a width of 20' per caster level at its terminus. Victims suffer [[/roll 1d20+10]] damage per caster level with no save (roll [[/roll 1d20]] per caster level, then add 10 x CL).","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":2,"range":[34,35],"drawn":false},{"_id":"D97vCiGtLDHS6g4L","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The caster creates a vicious ice storm that affects an area 100 yards in diameter. In addition to inflicting [[/roll 6d10]]+CL points of damage on creatures within the area of effect, the storm destroys crops, causes roofs to collapse, freezes rivers, chokes roads with ice, and produces other destruction at the judge's discretion. The ice storm lasts for 1 hour per caster level, though the mundane ice that is created may take longer to melt.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":2,"range":[36,37],"drawn":false},{"_id":"xgyxQ1yFf5Ss4ON3","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The caster creates a vicious ice storm that affects an area 1 mile in diameter for each level the caster possesses. In addition to inflicting [[/roll 6d10]]+CL points of damage on creatures within the area of effect, the storm destroys crops, causes roofs to collapse, freezes rivers, chokes roads with ice, and produces other destruction at the judge's discretion. The ice storm lasts for 1 hour per caster level, though the mundane ice that is created may take longer to melt.","img":"icons/sv