 to his patron, who will call in the debt at some point.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[24,27],"drawn":false},{"_id":"iaJ0u92ucVkVGzFl","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The patron considers the caster indispensable to his long-term goals. The caster learns the spell invoke patron as it relates to his patron and may cast it up to three times per day at a +1 bonus to the spell check. The patron also gives the caster a gift (for which a counter-gift is to be expected, of course). The gift is a single patron spell, selected from the patrons spell list. The caster can cast this spell once per day in place of a casting of invoke patron. Each time he casts this patron spell or invoke patron, the caster is indebted to his patron, who will call in the debt at some point.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[28,29],"drawn":false},{"_id":"kXl4uCbh7GOdSsZk","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The casters patron considers him indispensable to his long-term goals. The caster learns the spell invoke patron as it relates to his patron and may cast it up to three times per day at a +2 bonus to the spell check. The patron also gives the caster a gift (for which a counter-gift is to be expected, of course). The gift is a single patron spell, selected from the patrons spell list. The caster can cast this spell once per day in place of a casting of invoke patron. Each time he casts this patron spell or invoke patron, the caster is indebted to the patron, who will call in the debt at some point.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[30,31],"drawn":false},{"_id":"lJ5FdAmtwCbxgnJo","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The patron considers the caster integral to his long-term goals. The caster learns the spell invoke patron as it relates to his patron and may cast it up to four times per day at a +2 bonus to the spell check. The patron also gives the caster a gift (for which a counter-gift is to be expected, of course)